2011年8月4日，29岁英国黑人男子马克·达根（{{lang|en|Mark Duggan}}）是一名在册的黑幫成員，他在[[托特纳姆|托特纳姆]]運輸槍械的過程中被警方开枪射杀。[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]表示警方涉嫌策划袭击，怀疑他持有手枪，便试图将他逮捕。达根胸部中枪身亡。达根的死因引起托特纳姆民众的公开抗议<ref name=prasad />，活动随后演变成警民冲突，最终激化为[[2011年英国骚乱|全伦敦及英国其他城市的骚乱]]<ref name="lewis" />。

达根是伦敦警察厅分支部门{{le|三叉戟行动 (伦敦警察厅)|Operation Trident (Metropolitan Police)|三叉戟行动}}的调查对象，因持有BBM Bruni 92型手枪（[[貝瑞塔92手槍|贝瑞塔92]]的[[空包弹|空包弹]]版本，经改装可发射实弹）被警方了解。该手枪是凯文·哈钦森-福斯特（{{lang|en|Kevin Hutchinson-Foster}}）在达根遭杀害的15分钟前给他的。哈钦森-福斯特的审判于2012年9月至10月举行，陪审团未能定罪。2013年1月31日的重审中，哈钦森-福斯特因向达根提供枪手被定罪，背叛监禁。{{tsl|en|Independent Police Complaints Commission|警察独立投诉委员会}}一直调查该案件，但调查报告的发布推迟了一年多的时间。达根死因的{{tsl|en|Inquests in England and Wales|英格兰与威尔士讯问制度|公开审讯}}于2013年9月16日开始，2014年1月8日结束，裁判以8比2的结果裁定达根属[[自卫杀人|自卫杀人]]<ref name="Inquest conclusion">{{cite news|title=Mark Duggan inquest latest|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-25648913|accessdate=2014-01-08|newspaper=BBC Online|date=2014-01-08|archive-date=2014-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109152922/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-25648913|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

官方对达根死因的表述屡次变动<ref name=":0" /><ref name="guardianconf" />，招致各利益方及其他支持者的批评和怀疑<ref name="Briggs" />。

==背景==
1981年9月15日<ref name="G profile"/>，马克·达根于伦敦北部的{{le|阔水农场|Broadwater Farm}}出生，并在此处成长。父母是[[爱尔兰人|爱尔兰]]和{{tsl|en|British African-Caribbean people|英国非裔加勒比人|非裔加勒比人}}的后代<ref name=bfarm>{{cite news|title=Shot man who sparked violence grew up on Broadwater Farm|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/uk/crime/article3118087.ece|date=2012-02-29|work=The Times (London)|author=Sean O'Neill {{Relevance inline|date=2012年11月}}|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2017-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305092426/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/uk/crime/article3118087.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12岁至17岁时，达根与[[曼彻斯特|曼彻斯特]]的姨妈卡罗尔（{{lang|en|Carole}}）共同生活<ref name=profile>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-25363828|title=BBC News - Profile: Who was Mark Duggan?|last=Prodger|first=Matt|date=2014-01-08|work=bbc.co.uk/news|accessdate=2014-01-08|archive-date=2014-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109152952/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-25363828|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而另一位姨妈朱莉（{{lang|en|Julie}}）后来嫁给了曼彻斯特的黑帮头目{{le|德斯蒙德·努南|Desmond Noonan}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/mark-duggan-noonan-london-riots-2011-8|title=The Man Whose Death Sparked The British Riots Was A Notorious Crime Lord's Nephew|last=Taylor|first=Adam|date=2011-08-12|work=Business Insider|accessdate=2011-08-13|archive-date=2012-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014222033/http://www.businessinsider.com/mark-duggan-noonan-london-riots-2011-8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

事发时，达根和长期伴侣西蒙妮·威尔逊（{{lang|en|Semone Wilson}}）生了三个孩子，分别10岁、7岁和18个月<ref name=bfarm />。之后与另一位女子生了第四个孩子<ref name=2sides>{{cite news|title=Two sides of a family man|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/uk/crime/article3157835.ece|date=2012-02-29|work=The Times (London)|author=Fay Schlesinger|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2015-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125235517/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/news/uk/crime/article3157835.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>，还有第三位女子怀有他的儿子<ref>"Lawful Killing", BBC One, 5 December 2016</ref>。因此他是六个孩子的父亲，最年轻的一位在他去世时出生<ref name=profile/>。

表兄弟表示，达根曾在[[伦敦斯坦斯特德机场|伦敦斯坦斯特德机场]]工作，曾申请担任消防员<ref name=mourners>{{cite news|title=Mourners bid final farewell to shooting victim Mark Duggan |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/mourners-bid-final-farewell-to-shooting-victim-mark-duggan-2351883.html |date=2011-09-09 |work=The Independent (London) |author=Tom Morgan |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125031202/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/mourners-bid-final-farewell-to-shooting-victim-mark-duggan-2351883.html |archivedate=2014-01-25 }}</ref>。达根的儿子凯马尼（{{lang|en|Kemani}}）是伦敦{{le|钻头音乐|Drill music|钻头}}{{le|嘻哈群体|Hip-hop collective}}{{le|有机农场男孩|OFB (group)}}成员，艺名班多凯（{{lang|en|Bandokay}}）<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/sep/06/uk-drill-rappers-ofb-no-one-helps-us-round-here-music-is-the-only-way|title=UK drill rappers OFB: 'No one helps us round here. Music is the only way'|last=Thapar|first=Ciaran|date=2019-09-06|work=The Guardian|access-date=2019-12-13|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217134655/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2019/sep/06/uk-drill-rappers-ofb-no-one-helps-us-round-here-music-is-the-only-way|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《{{le|伦敦标准晚报|London Evening Standard}}》汤尼·汤普森（{{lang|en|Tony Thompson}}）认为，达根可能是{{le|托特纳姆庄园|Tottenham Mandem}}帮<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/mark-duggan-loving-family-man-or-violent-armed-thug-who-led-a-double-life/story-e6frg6so-1226111938510|title=Mark Duggan: loving family man or violent, armed thug who led a double life?|last=Schlesinger|first=Fay|author2=O'Neill, Sean|date=2011-08-10|work=The Australian|accessdate=2011-08-13|archive-date=2011-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810043132/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/mark-duggan-loving-family-man-or-violent-armed-thug-who-led-a-double-life/story-e6frg6so-1226111938510|dead-url=no}}</ref>北伦敦分支“星帮”（{{lang|en|Star Gang}}）的元老<ref name="thompson-revenge">{{cite news|first=Tony|last=Thompson|work=Evening Standard|title=When I grew up in Tottenham, we stole sweets; now it's revenge shootings|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/when-i-grew-up-in-tottenham-we-stole-sweets-now-its-revenge-shootings-6430928.html|date=2011-08-09|accessdate=2018-07-12|archive-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713165009/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/when-i-grew-up-in-tottenham-we-stole-sweets-now-its-revenge-shootings-6430928.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一位未具名的警方消息人士告诉《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》，达根是“非常出名的黑帮”<ref name="telegraph-man-killed" />，“骨干成员，托特纳姆的警方都知道”<ref name="whitehead-gangster">{{cite news |first=Tom |last=Whitehead |title=Dead man Mark Duggan was a known gangster who lived by the gun |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/8687403/London-riots-Dead-man-Mark-Duggan-was-a-known-gangster-who-lived-by-the-gun.html |work=The Telegraph |date=2011-08-08 |accessdate=2011-08-13 |archive-date=2011-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813025200/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/law-and-order/8687403/London-riots-Dead-man-Mark-Duggan-was-a-known-gangster-who-lived-by-the-gun.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

参与{{le|三叉戟帮犯罪指挥部|Trident Gang Crime Command|三叉戟行动}}的警察监视了达根。警方称怀疑达根正计划为同年3月在东伦敦的一家酒吧门外被捅死<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.tottenhamjournal.co.uk/news/neighbours_tributes_to_murdered_tottenham_rapper_everyone_loved_1_848129 |title=Neighbours' tributes to murdered Tottenham rapper 'everyone loved' |first=Emma |last=Youle |work=Tottenham& Wood Green Journal |date=2011-03-31 |accessdate=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110823111728/http://www.tottenhamjournal.co.uk/news/neighbours_tributes_to_murdered_tottenham_rapper_everyone_loved_1_848129 |archive-date=2011-08-23 |dead-url=yes  }}</ref>的表兄凯尔文·伊斯顿（{{lang|en|Kelvin Easton}}）<ref name="lewis-code" />报仇。周围人表示，自从表兄死后，达根越来越偏执<ref name="bbc-minicab">{{cite news |title=Tottenham police shooting: Dead man was minicab passenger |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14423942 |work=BBC |date=2011-08-05 |accessdate=2011-08-14 |archive-date=2011-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806204051/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14423942 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《每日电讯报》表示，根据该帮派的《街头法则》，达根必须为表兄的死报仇<ref name="lewis-code">{{cite news |first=Jason |last=Lewis |title=The street code of vengeance that sparked the riots |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8699857/The-street-code-of-vengeance-that-sparked-the-riots.html |work=The Telegraph |date=2011-08-13 |accessdate=2011-08-13 |archive-date=2011-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818095832/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8699857/The-street-code-of-vengeance-that-sparked-the-riots.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

事发后，警方及其他人士称达根为{{tsl|en|illegal drug trade|毒品交易|毒贩}}，但被家人和朋友否认<ref name="guardian" />。家人们表示针对达根的指控“子虚乌有”，达根“不是黑帮成员，没有前科”<ref name="townsend-trust" />。然而达根曾因持有大麻和{{tsl|en|handling stolen goods|销赃}}被判刑<ref name="bbc2013-criminalrecord">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-24210480|title=Duggan 'one of 48 most violent'|date=2013-09-23|via=www.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2019-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716011703/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-24210480|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的未婚妻表示他曾归所盗窃的财务<ref name="G profile">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/08/mark-duggan-profile-tottenham-shooting|title=Mark Duggan: profile of Tottenham police shooting victim|first1=Patrick|last1=Barkham|first2=Jon|last2=Henley|date=2011-08-08|website=the Guardian|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2019-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724231119/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/08/mark-duggan-profile-tottenham-shooting|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==案件==
[[File:Ferry_Lane,_Tottenham_Hale_-_geograph.org.uk_-_1767129.jpg|thumb]]

伦敦警察厅的警察于英国标准时间2011年8月4日晚6点15分截停了载有达根的私人出租车<ref>{{cite web|url=http://australianetworknews.com/stories/201108/3292491.htm?desktop|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120701135847/http://australianetworknews.com/stories/201108/3292491.htm?desktop|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-07-01|title=Fifth death in British riots|date=2011-08-12|work=australianetworknews.com|accessdate=2011-08-18}}</ref>。车辆被截停的地方无监控摄像头<ref>{{cite web |last1=Scott |first1=Stanford |title=Mark Duggan shooting: give the IPCC the powers it needs to investigate |url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/apr/27/mark-duggan-shooting-ipcc-investigate |website=The Guardians |accessdate=2020-07-28 |date=2012-04-27 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728172042/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/apr/27/mark-duggan-shooting-ipcc-investigate |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年9月，一名未具名的武装警察在凯文·哈钦森-福斯特的庭审中表示，达根走出车外，拔出系在腰部的自动装填手枪<ref name=waistband>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19662526|date=2012-09-20|work=BBC|title=Mark Duggan 'pulled gun from waistband'|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2019-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716010303/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19662526|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在询问中作证的匿名出租车司机表示，达根离开车子后跑了：

{{cquote|车子被截停后，几位手中拿着枪的男子迅速逃跑。那时我听到后车门打开的声音，便发现马克·达根走出车跑了。这个时候，我就听到前面有枪声，看到马克·达根中枪倒在地上。马克·达根中枪时，离我的车子仅2到3英尺。那时有一个男人走过来，打开了我的车门，非常气愤地抓住我的胳膊拽我出车子，把我扔在后轮胎旁边的地上。<ref name="taxi-driver" /><ref name=news_taxi_driver>{{cite news|url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/10/14/mark-duggan-minicab-driver-officers-said-theyd-shoot-me-too-4146204|title=London riots: Mark Duggan died of gunshot wound to chest, inquest told|work=Metro|date=2013-10-14|accessdate=2015-08-01}}</ref>}}

司机告诉法庭，武装警察曾威胁开枪打他，如果他继续看达根倒在地上的地方，表示警察严厉呵斥他。

警察开了两枪，一枪打在达根的[[肱二头肌|肱二头肌]]，一枪打中胸部。现场有一把枪<ref name=waistband />。{{le|伦敦救护服务|London Ambulance Service}}的护理人员和{{le|伦敦空中急救|London's Air Ambulance}}的医护人员抵达现场，但于英国标准时间18点41分宣布达根已死亡<ref name="ipic" /><ref name="wound">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/09/london-riots-mark-duggan-inquest|title=London riots: Mark Duggan died of gunshot wound to chest, inquest told|date=2011-08-09|work=The Guardian|location=UK|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-date=2014-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109192831/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/09/london-riots-mark-duggan-inquest|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

打死达根的警察隶属于[[特種槍械司令部|特種槍械司令部]]，三叉戟行动的警察陪同在侧<ref name="guardian">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/08/mark-duggan-profile-tottenham-shooting |title=Mark Duggan: profile of Tottenham police shooting victim |author1=Patrick Barkham |author2=Jon Henley |date=2011-08-08 |work=The Guardian |location=UK |accessdate=2011-08-08 |archive-date=2019-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724231119/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/08/mark-duggan-profile-tottenham-shooting |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一位目击着告诉《[[独立报|独立报]]》，达根中枪时被警察压制在地上<ref name="tpeck">{{cite web |last1=Peck |first1=Tom |title=A death at the hands of police – and a vigil that turned to |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/a-death-at-the-hands-of-police-ndash-and-a-vigil-that-turned-to-violence-2333590.html |website=The Independent |accessdate=2020-07-28 |date=2011-08-08 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728204400/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/a-death-at-the-hands-of-police-ndash-and-a-vigil-that-turned-to-violence-2333590.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在询问中被证据反驳。《每日电讯报》引述另一名目击者，一名警察“喝止男子‘数次’，但他未遵从警告”<ref name="telegraph-man-killed">{{cite news |title=Man killed in shooting incident involving police officer |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8682655/Mark-Duggan-killed-in-shooting-incident-involving-police-officer.html |work=The Telegraph |date=2011-08-04 |accessdate=2011-08-15 |archive-date=2011-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813163208/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8682655/Mark-Duggan-killed-in-shooting-incident-involving-police-officer.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]引述另一名目击者，指警察打枪前喊了两次“把枪放下”<ref name="witness-emerges">{{cite news|date=2012-04-26|accessdate=2012-04-26|title=Duggan shooting witness emerges|work=BBC|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-17859958|archive-date=2012-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426180806/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-17859958|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，接载达根的出租车司机告诉法庭，警方是无预警开枪<ref name=news_taxi_driver/>。{{tsl|en|Metropolitan Police Federation|大都会警察联合会}}代表表示，枪杀达根的警察“非常相信他和同事面临着眼看着会被枪杀的危险”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8697208/UK-riots-Mark-Duggan-was-nephew-of-Manchester-gangster-Desmond-Noonan.html|title=UK riots: Mark Duggan was nephew of Manchester gangster Desmond Noonan|date=2011-08-12|work=telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2011-08-31|archive-date=2011-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111018171347/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8697208/UK-riots-Mark-Duggan-was-nephew-of-Manchester-gangster-Desmond-Noonan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

其中一位包围达根的警察被子弹击中，之后子弹卡在电台中。该子弹由代号为V53的警察射出，穿过了达根的胳膊，射中这位警方<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2014/jan/08/mark-duggan-death-london-riots|title=Mark Duggan's death: two shots fired and two conflicting stories|first=Vikram|last=Dodd|date=2014-01-08|website=the Guardian|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728172859/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2014/jan/08/mark-duggan-death-london-riots|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中枪的警察被送往医院，当天晚上便出院<ref name=Pears>Elizabeth Pears, "[http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/man-shot-police-was-friends-nightclub-stab-victim Man 'Shot By Police' Was Friends With Nightclub Stab Victim] {{Wayback|url=http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/man-shot-police-was-friends-nightclub-stab-victim |date=20180314175755 }}", ''The Voice'', 5 August 2011.</ref>。

===警方后续行动===
警方着手移动了接载达根的出租车<ref name=guardianconf/>。就车辆何时移动进行一番争论后，警方将出租车送去检验，随后再送回现场<ref>Sandra Laville, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/24/mark-duggan-investigation-undermined Mark Duggan investigation undermined by 'inaccuracies'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/24/mark-duggan-investigation-undermined |date=20200728173442 }}", ''The Guardian'', 24 November 2011. [https://web.archive.org/web/20120406072514/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/nov/24/mark-duggan-investigation-undermined Archived] 20 November 2012.</ref>。当地一名平等机会倡导者表示，监警会最初不知道这些事情，后来才批准将车辆移走，然后要求将其带回到现场<ref name=Scott/>。

最初由代号“W70”的警察递交的“短版”事件报告并没有说达根举起了枪。W70在48小时后递交的另一份报告认为，达根从腰带抽出一把手枪。W70后来表示短版报告是“故意缩短”的<ref name=":0">Vikram Dodd, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/20/mark-duggan-had-gun-says-policeman Mark Duggan was shot after raising weapon, firearms officer tells court] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/20/mark-duggan-had-gun-says-policeman |date=20200728172053 }}", ''The Guardian'', 20 September 2012. [https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040032/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2012/sep/20/mark-duggan-had-gun-says-policeman Archived] 20 November 2012.</ref>。

直到达根遇害1天半后，警方才将死讯告诉他家人。警方后来为此致歉<ref>Akilah Russell, "[http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/police-apologise-duggan-family Police Apologise To Duggan Family] {{Wayback|url=http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/police-apologise-duggan-family |date=20171002184612 }}", ''The Voice'', 10 August 2011.</ref>。

===独立投诉委员会申诉===
{{le|独立警方投诉委员会|Independent Police Complaints Commission}}发言人最初表示“警察先中的枪，达根后中枪”<ref name="telegraph-man-killed" /><ref name="moore-bridger-shootout">{{cite news|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23975846-man-shot-dead-by-police-in-tottenham.do|title=Father dies and policeman hurt in 'terrifying' shoot-out|last=Moore-Bridger|first=Benedict|author2=Parsons, Rob|author3=Davenport, Justin|date=2011-08-05|work={{tsl|en|London Evening Standard||London Evening Standard}}|location=UK|accessdate=2011-08-09|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111122031542/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23975846-man-shot-dead-by-police-in-tottenham.do|archivedate=2011-11-22}}</ref>，但警方后来澄清该说法不属实<ref name=guardianconf /><ref name=Mirror12Dec11 />。有一颗子弹打进了警方佩戴的无线电，[[弹道学|弹道学]]测试显示子弹属{{le|披甲弹|jacketed round}}，或是警方[[HK_MP5冲锋枪|HK MP5]]半自动卡宾枪发射的子弹<ref name="ipic"/>，子弹可能是在{{le|跳弹|ricochet}}或[[停止作用|停止作用]]的影响下穿入无线电<ref name=Laville07 >{{cite news |title=Doubts emerge over Duggan shooting as London burns |author=Sandra Laville |author2=Paul Lewis |author3=Vikram Dodd |author4=Vikram Dodd |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/07/police-attack-london-burns |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2011-08-07 |accessdate=2011-08-07 |archive-date=2013-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930191543/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/07/police-attack-london-burns |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Gabbatt">{{cite news |title=London disturbances – Sunday 7 August |author1=Adam Gabbatt |author2=Ben Quinn |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/blog/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-police-duggan-live#block-44 |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2011-08-07 |accessdate=2011-08-09 |archive-date=2013-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002172405/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/blog/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-police-duggan-live#block-44 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

投诉委员会委托{{tsl|en|Forensic Science Service|法医处}}对手枪进行测试，得到的建议是手枪属非法枪械<ref name="ipic" /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8699857/The-street-code-of-vengeance-that-sparked-the-riots.html|title=The street code of vengeance that sparked the riots|last=Lewis|first=Jason|date=2011-08-13|work=telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2011-08-18|archive-date=2011-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818095832/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8699857/The-street-code-of-vengeance-that-sparked-the-riots.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23976974-no-evidence-that-mark-duggan-shot-at-police-says-ipcc.do |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120919080804/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23976974-no-evidence-that-mark-duggan-shot-at-police-says-ipcc.do |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2012-09-19 |title='No evidence' that Mark Duggan shot at police, says IPCC |date=2011-08-10 |work=London Evening Standard |accessdate=2011-08-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/264057/UK-riots-Mark-Duggan-had-a-loaded-pistol-|title=UK RIOTS: MARK DUGGAN 'HAD A LOADED PISTOL'|date=2011-08-10|work=express.co.uk|accessdate=2011-08-18|archive-date=2011-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816020448/http://www.express.co.uk/posts/view/264057/UK-riots-Mark-Duggan-had-a-loaded-pistol-|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Martin|last=Bentham|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23977786-mark-duggans-uncle-was-gang-boss-with-more-guns-than-the-police.do|title=Mark Duggan's uncle was gang boss 'with more guns than the police'|date=2011-08-12|accessdate=2011-08-16|work=Evening Standard|location=London|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813145649/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23977786-mark-duggans-uncle-was-gang-boss-with-more-guns-than-the-police.do|archivedate=2011-08-13}}</ref>。枪被一只袜子套住，按照推测，如果这把枪被用过，可能是枪手想避免留下证据<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23977786-mark-duggans-uncle-was-gang-boss-with-more-guns-than-the-police.do|title=Mark Duggan's uncle was gang boss 'with more guns than the police'|last=Bentham|first=Martin|date=2011-08-12|work=London Evening Standard|accessdate=2011-08-18|dead-url=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110813145649/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard/article-23977786-mark-duggans-uncle-was-gang-boss-with-more-guns-than-the-police.do|archivedate=2011-08-13}}</ref>。投诉委员会8月9日宣布未找到枪支有被用过的证据，但是没有排除对这把枪的怀疑，后续测试正在进行<ref name="ipic">{{cite web|url=http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_090811_dugganupdate.aspx|title=Update on Mark Duggan investigation including details of ballistic tests|date=2011-08-09|work=ipcc.gov.uk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006075848/http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_090811_dugganupdate.aspx|archive-date=2012-10-06|dead-url=yes|accessdate=2011-08-11}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Gang suspect killed by police did not fire his gun, tests show | first=Richard | last=Hall | work=The Independent | accessdate=2011-08-11 | url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/gang-suspect-killed-by-police-did-not-fire-his-gun-tests-show-2335134.html | date=2011-08-10 | archive-date=2011-09-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913190315/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/gang-suspect-killed-by-police-did-not-fire-his-gun-tests-show-2335134.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=bbc1>{{Cite news| title = Mark Duggan death: 'No evidence' Tottenham man opened fire| work = BBC| location = London| date = 2011-08-09| accessdate = 2011-08-11| url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14459516| archive-date = 2011-08-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110811113435/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14459516| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2011年11月18日，投诉委员会宣布与案件有关的9毫米手枪在距现场{{Convert|10|feet|meters}}到{{Convert|14|feet|meters}}英尺远的栅栏另一侧被发现<ref name=Dodd18Nov2011>Vikram Dodd, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/18/mark-duggan-ipcc-investigation-riots New questions raised over Duggan shooting] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/18/mark-duggan-ipcc-investigation-riots |date=20200728172411 }}", ''The Guardian'', 18 November 2011. Archived [https://web.archive.org/web/20121114124921/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/nov/18/mark-duggan-ipcc-investigation-riots 20 November 2012].</ref><ref name="v53"/>。达根家聘请的[[大律师|大律师]]{{le|迈克尔·曼斯菲尔德|Michael Mansfield}}表示，目击者告诉他，警方把枪扔过栅栏<ref name=guardianconf>{{Cite news | title= Mark Duggan's family have little confidence in police probe, court hears | work= [[衛報|The Guardian]] | author1= Vikram Dodd | author2= Diane Taylor | date= 2011-12-12 | accessdate= 2012-10-01 | url= https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/dec/12/mark-duggan-family-police-court | archive-date= 2014-01-11 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140111200558/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/dec/12/mark-duggan-family-police-court | dead-url= no }}</ref>。投诉委员会最初也说有三位警察目击到警察扔枪，但后来撤回该说法<ref name=Scott/>。

2011年11月18日，投诉委员会宣布调查案发六天前7月29日的一起事件中是否出现了同一把枪。当天，理发师彼得·奥萨德贝（Peter Osadebay）在哈克尼被30岁的凯文·哈钦森-福斯特（Kevin Hutchinson-Foster）袭击，哈克尼攻击前，曾拿出一把枪炫耀<ref name="bbc-gun">{{cite news|date=2011-11-18|title=Metropolitan Police probed over 'Mark Duggan gun' incident|accessdate=2011-11-18|work=BBC|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-15796551|archive-date=2011-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111118173419/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-15796551|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年1月13日，福斯特被裁定向达根提供枪击，庭审中他承认达根所用的枪和他打奥萨德贝的枪是同一把<ref name="hutchinson-guilty">{{cite news|title=Hutchinson-Foster guilty of supplying gun|work=BBC News|date=2013-01-31|accessdate=2014-01-11|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21176207|archive-date=2013-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602092745/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21176207|dead-url=no}}</ref>。达根的指纹也出现在一个纸板箱中，显示他用箱子装过枪。箱子在案发现场{{Convert|20|feet|meters}}处，里面有一只装着手枪的袜子。指纹和DNA未从手枪和袜子上检测出<ref>{{Cite news| last = Dodd| first = Vikram| title = Revealed: Mark Duggan was not armed when shot by police| work = The Guardian| accessdate = 2011-11-19| date = 2011-11-19| url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/18/mark-duggan-ipcc-investigation-riots| archive-date = 2014-01-09| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140109021122/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/18/mark-duggan-ipcc-investigation-riots| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=Guard25Mar13 />。其他测试显示达根身上没有枪伤的残留痕迹<ref name=Guard25Mar13 />。

=== 伦敦警察厅 ===
警方认为执法人员不存在不当行为，但表示射杀达根的人没有携带实弹武器当值<ref name="#1">"[http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/officer-who-shot-mark-duggan-%E2%80%9Cwill-not%E2%80%9D-return-duty Officer Who Shot Mark Duggan 'Will Not' Return To Duty]", ''The Voice'', 8 September 2012.</ref>。行动中携带武器的警员自称V53，仅向独立投诉委员会提交书面声明，拒绝接受审讯<ref name="v53">{{cite news| url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9840073/Revealed-gang-rivalry-Mark-Duggan-and-the-unavenged-murder-behind-the-London-riots.html | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Gordon | last=Rayner | title=Revealed: gang rivalry, Mark Duggan and the unavenged murder behind the London riots | date=2013-01-31}}</ref><ref name = "ViDo26Apr2012">{{cite news |url= https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/apr/26/mark-duggan-met-refuse-ipcc |title= Mark Duggan death: Met officers refuse IPCC interviews |last= Dodd |first= Vikram |date= 2012-04-26 |publisher= guardian.co.uk |access-date= 2012-04-28 }}</ref>。投诉委员会请求审讯警方，就算他们没有犯罪嫌疑<ref name="#2">{{cite news|date=2012-04-26|access-date=2012-04-29|title=IPCC seeks increased powers to investigate police|work=BBC|first=Simon|last= Cox|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-17843690}}</ref>。

=== 凯文·哈钦森-福斯特的审判 ===
2011年11月，独立投诉委员会调查警方对2011年7月29日事件“调查响应的质量”<ref name="bbc-gun" />。

2012年9月18日，哈钦森-福斯特在斯尼亚斯布罗克的皇家法院受审。被告被控向达根提供作案用的BBM Bruni 92型手枪<ref name="H-F">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19635639|date=18 September 2012 |work=BBC|title=Mark Duggan 'given loaded gun' before police shooting}}</ref>，但他否认指控，解释了自己的DNA出现在枪上面的原因，声称自己曾被达根一伙黑帮用枪殴打<ref name=karma>{{cite news|date= 28 September 2012| access-date= 29 September 2012|title = Mark Duggan police shooting: Death was 'karma'|work=BBC| url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19765652}}</ref>。

庭审期间，{{tsl|en|QEB Hollis Whiteman (chambers)|QEB霍利斯·怀特曼}}的{{tsl|en|Edward Brown (barrister)|QC爱德华·布朗}}检察官争辩称达根去莱顿找哈钦森-福斯特拿枪，之后带着枪开车去托特纳姆<ref name="H-F"/>。警方认为达根是在中弹前的12到15分钟从哈钦森-福斯特处领到枪<ref name="#3">"[https://web.archive.org/web/20120919195453/http://voice-online.co.uk/article/duggan-was-%E2%80%98given-loaded-gun-minutes-being-killed%E2%80%99 Duggan Was 'Given Loaded Gun Minutes Before Being Killed]'", ''The Voice'', 18 September 2012.</ref>。

====警方证词====
七位警官用假名在庭上作证<ref name="#4">"[http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/police-keep-anonymity-duggan-gun-trial Police To Keep Anonymity In Duggan Gun Trial]", ''The Voice'', 27 July 2012.</ref>。警方声称达根从腰带拔出枪，用枪指着警察，之后被对方击毙<ref name="contact">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19718245|title=Duggan 'in contact' with accused|date=25 September 2012|via=www.bbc.co.uk}}</ref><ref name="holding-gun">{{cite news|first=Vikram|last=Dodd|title=Police marksman was 'absolutely certain' Mark Duggan was holding gun|work=The Guardian|date=26 September 2012|access-date=27 September 2012|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/26/mark-duggan-gun-crime}}</ref>。出租车司机递交证据，得到一名在场警察确认。证据显示，达根走下出租车，打算逃跑。司机表示“看到马克·达根下车逃跑。与此同时，我听到前面有枪声，我看到马克·达根中了枪，他倒在地上<ref name="taxi-driver" />”，“马克·达根中枪的时候，离我的车只有两到三英尺”<ref name=news_taxi_driver/>。

====病理学家证词====
负责检验达根遗体的病理学家西蒙·波尔（Simon Poole）在2013年1月凯文·哈钦森-福斯特案重审时作证，声称达根在事件中受的伤与开枪警官的证词不一致。代表哈钦森-福斯特的大律师质疑波尔，认为警方子弹穿透波尔右侧的身体，之后从右侧转移到左侧。波尔同意大律师的说法：“所以说那种情况不合理，是吧？警察开枪打中他左侧的身体，子弹穿透达根先生的胸口，理应从左侧去到右侧，但它是右侧去到左侧。所以可以说那种情况不合理？<ref name=BBC17Jan13>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21060194|title= Police account of Mark Duggan's injuries 'differs' from pathologist| work=BBC|date=17 January 2013|access-date=22 January 2013}}</ref>”但波尔后来认同检方的意见，就是达根如果正面朝向开枪的警察，则他与警察的相对位置就会改变<ref name=BBC17Jan13 />。2011年12月独立投诉委员会的声明引述波尔的说法，即在达根的手臂处找到第二枚卡住的子弹<ref name=Mirror12Dec11>"Mark Duggan inquiry: Police watchdog investigator admits 'mistake' over information that Duggan fired at officers first", ''Daily Mirror'', 12 December 2011; see "[http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_12112011_duggan_statement.aspx?auto=True&l1link=pages%2Fnews.aspx&l1title=News%20and%20press&l2link=news%2FPages%2Fdefault.aspx&l2title=Press%20Releases Statement intended to be read out to HM Coroner at pre-inquest hearing into death of Mark Duggan]".</ref>。

====结果====
2012年10月17日，陪审团未能达成有罪判决<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19978769|date=17 October 2012|title=Mark Duggan: No verdict in Kevin Hutchinson-Foster gun trial|work=BBC}}</ref>。重审日期定于2013年1月，之后被告被判向达根提供手枪<ref>{{cite news| date=31 January 2013 | access-date=31 January 2013|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21176207|title=Hutchinson-Foster guilty of supplying gun|work=BBC}}</ref>，2月26日获刑11年，其中提供枪支7年，相关罪行4年<ref>{{cite news|last= Press Association |work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2013/feb/26/man-gave-gun-mark-duggan|title=Man who gave gun to Mark Duggan jailed for 11 years|date=26 February 2013|access-date=26 February 2013}}</ref>。但是哈钦森-福斯特的案件未能释除大众对达根遇害的众多谜团<ref name=Guard31Jan13>Vikram Dodd, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2013/jan/31/mark-duggan-shooting-mystery-gun-arrest Mark Duggan shooting still a mystery despite gun supplier verdict: Kevin Hutchinson-Foster's guilt does little to clarify events that triggered Duggan being stopped and shot dead by police]", ''The Guardian'', 31 January 2013.</ref>。

==后续==
达根的死讯迅速传开。达根被枪击后不久，Facebook上流传据称警方踩着达根尸体的照片。仇警情绪迅速蔓延<ref name=Briggs>Daniel Briggs, "Frustrations, urban relations and temptations: contextualising the social disorder in London"; in ''The English riots of 2011: a summer of discontent'', ed. Daniel Briggs; Hampshire: Waterside Press, 2012.</ref>。

===示威活动===
====警民关系紧张====
自1985年{{tsl|en|Broadwater Farm riot|宽水农场骚乱}}以来，黑人社群与警方的关系长期剑拔弩张<ref name="jackson">{{cite news |title=London riots: Tensions behind unrest revealed |first=Peter |last=Jackson |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14436529 |work=BBC News |location=London |date=2011-08-07 |access-date=2011-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809025110/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-14436529 |archive-date=2011-08-09 |url-status=dead}}</ref>，托特纳姆工党议员{{tsl|en|David Lammy|大卫·拉米}}认为“警方与（黑人）社群之间早已存在的裂痕已经扩大”<ref>{{cite news|last=Lammy|first=David|title=Tottenham riot: The lesson of Broadwater Farm|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riot-broadwater-farm|access-date=2012-04-02|newspaper=guardian.co.uk|date=2011-08-07}}</ref>。他表示，1985年以来当地社群与警方的关系有所改善<ref name="newton-answers">{{cite news|first=Simon |last=Newton |url=http://news.sky.com/home/uk-news/article/16045172 |title=Tottenham Burns: Rioting Erupts On Streets |work=Sky |location=London |date=2011-08-07 |access-date=2011-08-17 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111201060051/http://news.sky.com/home/uk-news/article/16045172 |archive-date=2011-12-01 }}</ref>，但此次枪击案让紧张关系“再度升温”<ref>{{cite news|date=2011-08-07|access-date=2011-08-15|first=Andy|last=Moore|work=BBC|title=Riots in Tottenham after Mark Duggan shooting protest|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14434318}}</ref>，达根的死只是“托特纳姆民众在被警方拘禁时死亡的其中一环”<ref name="hattenstone-lammy">{{cite news |first=Simon|last=Hattenstone|title=David Lammy: 'There is a history in Tottenham that involves deaths in police custody'|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2011/aug/14/david-lammy-tottenham-mark-duggan|date=2011-08-14|access-date=2011-08-16}}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Operation Trident (Metropolitan Police)|三叉戟行动}}主席{{tsl|en|Claudia Webbe|克劳迪娅·韦伯}}直言许多黑人认为达根枪击案是“又是一起被拘禁人士无辜死亡的事件”<ref name="webbe-justice">{{cite news|first=Claudia|last=Webbe|url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riot-community-destruction|title=Tottenham's violence was wrong. Now police need to show justice is being done|work=The Guardian|location=London|date=2011-08-07|access-date=2011-08-17}}</ref>，托特纳姆黑人青年“被拦截搜身的仍然是白人青年的六、七、八倍”<ref>{{cite news|first=Matthew|last=Connolly|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2011/aug/16/riots-tensions-previous-decades-smoulder
|title=Do riots show that tensions of earlier decades still smoulder?|work=The Guardian|location=London|date=2011-08-16|access-date=2011-08-17}}</ref>。

英国黑人小说家{{tsl|en|Alex Wheatle|亚历克斯·惠特尔}}曾因参与{{tsl|en|1981 Brixton riot|1981年布里克斯顿暴乱}}要服刑<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/comment/columnists/charlesmoore/8410373/Things-the-BBC-didnt-tell-us-about-the-Brixton-riots.html|title=Things the BBC didn't tell us about the Brixton riots|last=Moore|first=Charles|date=2011-03-28|work=telegraph.co.uk|access-date=2011-08-21}}</ref>，他表示许多黑人同胞在被警方拘禁期间死亡，但警察从未被定罪，“令人深感愤怒”<ref name="wheatle-answers">{{cite news|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/we-need-answers-about-the-death-of-mark-duggan-6430467.html|title=We need answers about the death of Mark Duggan|last=Wheatle|first=Alex|date=2011-08-09|access-date=2018-07-12}}</ref>。

2017年，提议用子弹杀死达根的警察托尼·汉利（Tony Hanley）精神崩溃，故意让警察开枪打死自己，最终饮弹自尽。汉利说经常看到达根的鬼魂，认为自己要对达根负责<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2017/nov/03/police-officer-says-he-thought-met-armourer-wanted-to-be-shot-dead|title=Police officer says he thought Met armourer wanted to be shot dead|first=Damien|last=Gayle|date=2017-11-03|website=the Guardian}}</ref>。

====骚乱====
{{main|2011年英国骚乱}}
[[File:Reeves_furniture_store_burnt_out.jpg|thumb]]
英国标准时间2011年8月6日17点30分，达根的亲属和当地居民从{{tsl|en|Broadwater Farm|宽水农场}}游行到托特纳姆警察局。示威者高呼“我们要答案”，要求警方公开达根之死的信息。他们还提出要求“正义”的进一步要求，让更多人知道他们社区的警民关系紧张<ref name=Briggs/>。警察局长与示威者对话，但被要求见上司。晚上8点，一名16岁的女孩接近警方，疑似投掷传单或石头。警方携带盾牌和警棍包括这个女孩，据称打破了她的头<ref name=Lewis>Paul Lewis, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-peaceful-protest Tottenham riots: a peaceful protest, then suddenly all hell broke loose]", ''The Guardian'', 7 August 2011. [https://web.archive.org/web/20130218094330/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-peaceful-protest Archived] 20 November 2012.</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8687547/Attack-on-teenage-girl-blamed-for-start-of-Tottenham-riot.html | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Martin | last=Beckford | title='Attack' on teenage girl blamed for start of Tottenham riot | date=2011-08-08}}</ref><ref>{{youtube|YX9qZVsMQP8|16 Year Old Girl Attacked by Tottenham Riot Police!}}</ref>。8点20分，正在等待警官出面的民众朝附近两辆警车纵火。大都会警察局局长阿德里安·汉斯托克表示暴力活动是由“不参与守夜活动的人士”挑起的<ref name="Gabbatt"/>。其他目击者表示集会最初大致和平，但有声音煽动集会人士攻击警察<ref>Mark Hughes, "[https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8687804/Tottenham-riot-bullet-lodged-in-officers-radio-at-time-of-Mark-Duggan-death-was-police-issue.html Tottenham riot: bullet lodged in officer's radio at time of Mark Duggan death 'was police issue']", ''The Telegraph'', 8 August 2011.</ref>。

暴力示威活动蔓延到伦敦其他地区乃至英格兰其他地方<ref name="lewis">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/07/tottenham-riots-peaceful-protest|title=Tottenham riots: a peaceful protest, then suddenly all hell broke loose|last=Lewis|first=Paul|date=2011-08-07|work=The Guardian |location=UK|access-date=2011-08-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2011/0809/breaking25.html|title=Timeline – British disorder by dates|date=2011-08-09|work=The Irish Times |access-date=2011-08-10}}</ref>。示威者声称暴力示威是由多种因素引起的，包括警察问题、贫穷及有色人种与警方关系紧张<ref name=prasad>{{cite news|newspaper=The Guardian|first=Rhaeka|last=Prasad|date=2011-12-04|title=Reading the riots: Rebels with a cause? Rioters claim 'payback' against the police: On the streets Those involved in the unrest speak of a common enemy – and a shared hatred of stop and search|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/dec/05/riots-revenge-against-police}}</ref><ref name=year>{{cite news|title=London riots – one year on: Owen Jones commences a series of special reports|first=Owen|last=Jones|newspaper=The Independent|date=2012-07-23|access-date=2012-11-20|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/london-riots--one-year-on-owen-jones-commences-a-series-of-special-reports-7965142.html}}</ref><ref name=age>{{cite news|newspaper=The Age|first=Michael|last=Green|date=2012-03-20|title=How did Michael Atakelt die?}}</ref>。

达根的家属谴责暴力行动。达根的哥哥表示“完全无法容忍任何类似的行为”<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/victims-family-condemn-riot-2333410.html|title=Victim's family condemn riot| work=The Independent| date= 2011-08-07| access-date=2011-08-11}}</ref>。达根的事件或许是诱发暴力行为的主要因素，[[英国首相|英国首相]][[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]否认杜根之死与随后的抢劫之间存在因果关系<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/mobile/uk-politics-14492789|title=Riots: David Cameron's Commons statement in full|publisher=BBC | date=2011-08-11}}</ref>。

===媒体报道===
达根的死很多成为媒体关注的焦点事件。最初[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]错误声称其中一枪是“从车内的非法枪支中射出的”<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14423942 | work=BBC News | title=Tottenham police shooting: Dead man was minicab passenger | date=2011-08-05}}</ref>。《[[独立报|独立报]]》在2014年1月8日表示“当局错误地说他是在交火中被击中的”<ref>[https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/mark-duggan-inquest-was-he-really-armed-were-the-police-under-threat-all-the-key-evidence-9046789.html Mark Duggan inquest key evidence: Was he really armed? Were the police under threat?]. ''The Independent''</ref>。部分媒体将达根描绘成黑帮分子，混淆不同媒体声称达根的犯罪记录有些或根本不存在的说法，而遭到批评<ref name="bbc2013-criminalrecord" /><ref name=voice2011>"[http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/how-media-shamefully-manipulated-mark-duggans-death How The Media Shamefully Manipulated Mark Duggan's Death]", ''The Voice'', 10 August 2011.</ref>。部分媒体因不加批判地报道了杜根先开枪的警方的假新闻，而受到指责<ref name=voice2011 />。骚乱事件引起国际社会关注达根的死亡，一名伊朗官员认为事件“严重侵犯人权”<ref>"Iran/United Kingdom: Iranian Legislator Condemns Blatant Violation of Human Rights in Britain", ''Asia News Monitor'', 12 August 2011; accessed [http://search.proquest.com/docview/889079191 via ProQuest].</ref>。

===葬礼===
2011年9月9日，达根的葬礼在[[伍德格林|伍德格林]]新约上帝教会（New Testament Church of God）举行。数千名的围观者观看了葬礼游行，警方低调布防<ref>{{cite news|title=Thousands gather for Mark Duggan funeral|first=Peter|last=Walker|author2=Hugh Muir |author3=Alexandra Topping|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/sep/09/mark-duggan-funeral-tottenham|date=2011-09-09|access-date=2011-09-09}}</ref>。

==调查==
===投诉委员会调查===
按照人员与警方接触后死亡或重伤的标准程序<ref name=bbc2>{{Cite news| title =Mark Duggan death: IPCC appeals for witnesses |work=BBC | location = London|date= 2011-08-11 | access-date =2011-08-11| url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14489165}}</ref>，事件很快便报告给了独立警察投诉委员会<ref name=bbc2nd>{{cite news |title=Man dead and police officer hurt in Tottenham shooting |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-14412752 |newspaper=BBC News |date=2011-08-05 |access-date=2011-08-06}}</ref>。投诉委员会的工作人员还调查了[[闭路电视|闭路电视]]片段、[[999_(求救電話)|999]]报警电话及电台录音<ref>{{cite news | title=Appeal over death that sparked riot | url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/local-national/uk/appeal-over-death-that-sparked-riot-16035614.html | newspaper=Belfast Telegraph |date=2011-08-12}}</ref>。

8月12日，投诉委员会表示他们事后可能向记者提供了错误的信息，让大家以为达根和警方交火。有枚子弹虽然卡在警方的无线电里，但没有证据显示这是达根枪开出的子弹<ref>{{cite web|title=Release of information in early stages of Mark Duggan investigation|url=http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_120811_Release-of-information-in-early-stages-of-Mark-Duggan.aspx|publisher=IPCC|access-date=2011-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111221090821/http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_120811_Release-of-information-in-early-stages-of-Mark-Duggan.aspx|archive-date=2011-12-21|url-status=dead}}</ref>。委员会还表示外界谣传达根被警方多次开枪爆头“处决”的消息不属实<ref name="cerfontyne-shooting">{{cite web|title=Statement from IPCC on Mark Duggan shooting|first=Rachel|last=Cerfontyne|date=2011-08-07|access-date=2011-08-19|work=IPCC|url=http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr070811_statement.aspx|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320161849/http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr070811_statement.aspx|archive-date=2012-03-20|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref name="chan4-prevented">{{cite news|url=http://www.channel4.com/news/could-the-tottenham-riots-have-been-prevented|work=Channel 4| date=2011-08-19| access-date=2011-08-19|title=Could the Tottenham riots have been prevented?}}</ref>。然而达根的家人不相信委员会的调查公平、独立，要求独立调查伦敦警察厅和委员会的关系，并呼吁让独立第三方进行第二次尸检<ref name="townsend-trust">{{cite news |first=Mark |last=Townsend|title=London riots: the family of Mark Duggan says it has no trust in the IPCC |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/14/mark-duggan-family-ipcc-met-police-tottenham-riots|work=The Guardian |date=2011-08-14 |access-date=2011-08-14}}</ref>。验尸官{{tsl|en|Andrew Walker (barrister)|安德鲁·沃克}}计划出席2011年12月12日的首次聆讯<ref name="wound"/>。

2011年11月，投诉委员会任命的两位“社区咨询小组”成员辞职，留下的其中一人表示“震惊地了解到独立委员会打破自己的规则，向记者提供错误的信息”，同时发现委员会调查“存在缺陷，很可能在一定程度上被玷污”，“意味着我们永远无法相信他们对杀人案的最终报告”<ref>{{cite news|work=The Guardian|title=Adviser quits Duggan inquiry with attack on 'shoddy investigation'|first=Vikram|last=Dodd|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/nov/20/mark-duggan-shooting-watchdog-panel|date=2011-11-21|access-date=2011-11-21}}</ref>。

2012年2月29日，投诉委员会维持认为伦敦警察厅没有合理告知家人达根的死讯。委员会调查明确没有提到2011年8月6日及之后的事件<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_290212_duggan.aspx|title=Loading site please wait...|website=www.ipcc.gov.uk}}</ref>。早在2011年8月，伦敦警察厅助理副警长史蒂夫·卡瓦纳（Steve Kavanagh）就警方最初与达根家人接触的方式不当，向他们道歉<ref>{{Cite news| last = Milmo| first = Cahal|author2=Rob Hastings|title = A dead man, a crucial question: should police have shot Mark Duggan? | work=The Independent| location = London|date= 2011-08-09 | access-date =2011-08-11| url = https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/crime/a-dead-man-a-crucial-question-should-police-have-shot-mark-duggan-2334133.html}}</ref>，认为投诉委员会有责任向达根的家人提供情报<ref name="dodd-apologise">{{cite news| first=Vikram|last=Dodd|title=Police apologise to Mark Duggan's family for failing to keep them informed|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2011/aug/08/police-apology-mark-duggan-shooting| work=The Guardian| location=London| date=2011-08-08|access-date=2011-08-13}}</ref>。3月底，投诉委员会表示按照《{{tsl|en|Regulation of Investigatory Powers Act 2000|2000年调查权力监管法}}》，他们不可能在调查期间对外公开消息，质疑对验尸官的聆讯是否可以公开进行<ref>{{Cite news| last = Malik| first = Shiv|author2=Sandra Laville| title = Mark Duggan death: IPCC says hands are tied over release of evidence| work = The Guardian| location = London| access-date = 2012-04-28| date = 2012-03-29| url = https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2012/mar/29/mark-duggan-death-ipcc-hands-tied-evidence}}</ref>。2012年4月，BBC公开案发后的现场画面，显示医护人员在现场处理达根的尸体。投诉委员会谴责BBC播出画面前没有问过他们<ref>"[http://www.voice-online.co.uk/article/witness-films-scenes-after-mark-duggan-was-shot Witness Films Scenes After Mark Duggan Was Shot]", ''The Voice'', 27 April 2012.</ref>。

投诉委员会计划于2012年夏季发布调查报告，但到2013年1月仍未发布，同时原计划进行的谋杀案聆讯推迟到9月进行<ref name=Guard28Jan13 />。2013年3月，投诉委员会表示会在4月发布报告，5月递交给聆讯法庭<ref name=Guard25Mar13 />。至于谋杀达根的警察，投诉委员会发言人于8月2日表示“现阶段未有证据表明有刑事行为”。他们透露调查已基本结束，最终报告将于8月晚些时候发布<ref name=Guardian2Aug2013>Vikram Dodd, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2013/aug/02/mark-duggan-shooting-inquiry-evidence Mark Duggan police shooting: IPCC inquiry finds no evidence of criminality: Shooter declined to answer questions orally, instead submitting written answers later]"; ''The Guardian'', 2 August 2013.</ref>。

11名涉事警察最初拒绝接受委员会问话。杀害达根的警察“V53”后来提交了书面证词<ref name=Guardian2Aug2013 />。

2019年12月，法医调查员呼吁重新调查2011年的案件，表示案件的虚拟模式与调查结果有所出入<ref name=GuardianModel>{{Cite news| issn = 0261-3077| last = Dodd| first = Vikram| title = Mark Duggan shooting report challenged by human rights groups| work = The Guardian| access-date = 2019-12-05| date = 2019-12-05| url = https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2019/dec/05/mark-duggan-shooting-report-challenged-by-human-rights-groups}}</ref>。他们的报告于2020年6月公布<ref>{{Cite news| last1 = Siddique| first1 = Haroon| last2 = Voce| first2 = Antonio| last3 = McMullan| first3 = Lydia| last4 = Hulley-Jones| first4 = Frank| title = Mark Duggan shooting: can forensic tech cast doubt on official report?| work = The Guardian| access-date = 2020-06-10| date = 2020-06-10| url = http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/ng-interactive/2020/jun/10/mark-duggan-shooting-can-forensic-tech-cast-doubt-on-official-report}}</ref>。从投诉委员会更名而来的{{tsl|en|Independent Office for Police Conduct|警察行为独立办公室}}于2021年5月表示不会重新调查案件，新报告未证明他们的调查出错<ref>{{cite web |last1=Siddique |first1=Haroon |title=Mark Duggan’s family: police ‘lack courage’ to reopen investigation  28 May 2021 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/may/28/mark-duggan-family-police-lack-courage-to-reopen-investigation |website=The Guardian |publisher=The Guardian |access-date=2021-05-30}}</ref>。

===伦敦警察厅===
警方认为涉事警察不存在不当行为，但表示击毙达根的警方之后不会持上膛武器当值<ref name="#1"/>。

代号V53的涉事持枪警察向独立投诉委员会提交书面声明，未接受询问<ref name="witness-emerges" /><ref name = "ViDo26Apr2012" />。托特纳姆议员{{tsl|en|David Lammy|大卫·拉米}}批评该警察的行为<ref name="v53">{{cite news| url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/9840073/Revealed-gang-rivalry-Mark-Duggan-and-the-unavenged-murder-behind-the-London-riots.html | work=The Daily Telegraph | first=Gordon | last=Rayner | title=Revealed: gang rivalry, Mark Duggan and the unavenged murder behind the London riots | date=2013-01-31}}</ref><ref name = "ViDo26Apr2012">{{cite news |url= https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/apr/26/mark-duggan-met-refuse-ipcc |title= Mark Duggan death: Met officers refuse IPCC interviews |last= Dodd |first= Vikram |date= 2012-04-26 |publisher= guardian.co.uk |access-date= 2012-04-28 }}</ref>。其实投诉委员会有权询问警方，即便他们没有犯罪嫌疑<ref name="#2"/>。

===Trial of Kevin Hutchinson-Foster===
In November 2011, the IPCC began an investigation into the "quality of the investigative response" by police to an incident on 29 July 2011, for which police charged Kevin Hutchinson-Foster with possession of a handgun, believing the gun may be the same found at the shooting of Mr. Duggan.<ref name="bbc-gun" />

On 18 September 2012, Hutchinson-Foster's trial commenced in the Crown Court at Snaresbrook. The defendant was charged with supplying Duggan with the BBM Bruni Model 92 handgun, found near Duggan's car after his death.<ref name="H-F">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19635639|date=2012-09-18 |work=BBC|title=Mark Duggan 'given loaded gun' before police shooting}}</ref> The defendant denied the charge and gave his explanation for the presence of his DNA on the gun by alleging he had been beaten with the weapon by a gang that included Duggan.<ref name=karma>{{cite news|date= 2012-09-28| access-date= 2012-09-29|title = Mark Duggan police shooting: Death was 'karma'|work=BBC| url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19765652}}</ref>

During the trial, prosecutor {{tsl|en|Edward Brown (barrister)||Edward Brown QC}} of {{tsl|en|QEB Hollis Whiteman (chambers)||QEB Hollis Whiteman}} contended that Duggan travelled to Leyton to collect the gun from Hutchinson-Foster, before driving to Tottenham with it.<ref name="H-F"/> The police alleged that Duggan had received a gun from Hutchinson-Foster 12–15 minutes before he was shot.<ref name="#3"/>

====Police testimony====
The trial included testimony from seven police officers who were allowed to remain anonymous and use pseudonyms.<ref name="#4"/> The Police alleged that Duggan had pulled the gun from his waistband and pointed it at police before they shot him.<ref name="contact">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19718245|title=Duggan 'in contact' with accused|date=2012-09-25|via=www.bbc.co.uk}}</ref><ref name="holding-gun">{{cite news|first=Vikram|last=Dodd|title=Police marksman was 'absolutely certain' Mark Duggan was holding gun|work=The Guardian|date=2012-09-26|access-date=2012-09-27|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/26/mark-duggan-gun-crime}}</ref>

According to the evidence given by the cab driver and corroborated by one policeman present at the scene, Duggan got out of the taxi and ran in an attempt to escape.<ref name="taxi-driver">{{cite news|title=Mark Duggan shooting: taxi driver tells court how police surrounded cab|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2012/sep/27/mark-duggan-shooting-taxi-driver-evidence|date=2012-09-27|access-date=2012-09-27|work=the Guardian}}</ref> The driver stated, "I saw that Mark Duggan got out and ran. At the same time, I heard firing from the front. I saw shots strike Mark Duggan. He fell to the ground."<ref name="taxi-driver" /> "Mark Duggan only got 2ft–3ft from my car when he was shot", the taxi driver later testified.<ref name=news_taxi_driver/>

====Pathologist testimony====
Simon Poole, a pathologist who had performed a post-mortem on Duggan's body, testified in January 2013 at the retrial of Kevin Hutchinson-Foster and asserted that the injuries Duggan sustained in the shooting were not consistent with the account of the incident that was given by the police officer who fired the lethal shot. Questioned by a barrister representing Hutchinson-Foster, Poole said that the police bullet had penetrated Duggan's body on the right side and travelled from right to left. Poole agreed with the barrister's statement: "So the scenario can't be right? The officer fires to his left and the bullet hits Mr Duggan in the chest and it should go from left to right – but it went right to left. Therefore the scenario can't be right?"<ref name=BBC17Jan13>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21060194|title= Police account of Mark Duggan's injuries 'differs' from pathologist| work=BBC|date=2013-01-17|access-date=2013-01-22}}</ref>

Poole also later agreed with the prosecution that if Duggan had turned to face the officer who shot him, his position relative to them would have changed.<ref name=BBC17Jan13 />

A December 2011 IPCC statement had cited Poole for discovering that a second bullet struck Duggan's arm.<ref name=Mirror12Dec11>"Mark Duggan inquiry: Police watchdog investigator admits 'mistake' over information that Duggan fired at officers first", ''Daily Mirror'', 12 December 2011; see "[http://www.ipcc.gov.uk/news/Pages/pr_12112011_duggan_statement.aspx?auto=True&l1link=pages%2Fnews.aspx&l1title=News%20and%20press&l2link=news%2FPages%2Fdefault.aspx&l2title=Press%20Releases Statement intended to be read out to HM Coroner at pre-inquest hearing into death of Mark Duggan]".</ref>

====Outcome====
On 17 October 2012, the jury failed to reach a verdict.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-19978769|date=2012-10-17|title=Mark Duggan: No verdict in Kevin Hutchinson-Foster gun trial|work=BBC}}</ref> The re-trial date was set for January 2013,<ref>{{cite news|date=2012-11-09|access-date=2013-01-22|title=Kevin Hutchinson-Foster retrial set for January| work=BBC|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-20268713}}</ref> and on 31 January 2013 the defendant was convicted of supplying Duggan with the handgun.<ref>{{cite news| date=2013-01-31 | access-date=2013-01-31|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-21176207|title=Hutchinson-Foster guilty of supplying gun|work=BBC}}</ref> On 26 February 2013, the defendant was sentenced to eleven years in prison; seven years for supplying the gun, four years for related offences.<ref>{{cite news|last= Press Association |work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2013/feb/26/man-gave-gun-mark-duggan|title=Man who gave gun to Mark Duggan jailed for 11 years|date=2013-02-26|access-date=2013-02-26}}</ref>

The Hutchinson-Foster case did not resolve a number of significant unknown questions related to the Duggan killing.<ref name=Guard31Jan13>Vikram Dodd, "[https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2013/jan/31/mark-duggan-shooting-mystery-gun-arrest Mark Duggan shooting still a mystery despite gun supplier verdict: Kevin Hutchinson-Foster's guilt does little to clarify events that triggered Duggan being stopped and shot dead by police]", ''The Guardian'', 31 January 2013.</ref>

